modDescription:
Building a doomsday bunker to withstand the inevitable nuke? You need egress points that can keep up!

Presenting smittylv’s newest mod, a pack of extremely tough Hermetic blast doors, [windows](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-windows/) and gates by smittylv.

## Includes

* 3x blast windows (1×1)
* 4x blast [doors](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-doors/) (2×1)
* 1x blast gate (4×3)
* 1x blast double door (2×2)

**[Download](https://drive.google.com/file/d/1owsRJf3_9ouJb1Mg7hVC07mQefLh0QPi/view?usp=sharing)**
